---
title: Monkfish, Bacon and Butternut Squash Risotto with Rocket Salad and Chilli Flakes
description: Risotto is the ultimate comfort food. This one boasts creamy rice studded with nuggets of bacon. Butternut squash brings a hint of sweetness and the chilli adds just the right amount of heat. Don't forget a squeeze of lemon juice to bring everything together!
